data.description: Welcome to your extraordinary 5-acre, 4 bed 2 bath haven at the end of Dayton Valley Road, where spacious living meets privacy and endless recreational possibilities. Single-level, 2066 sq ft features 3/4" Brazilian Santos Mahogany hardwood flooring, french doors to a master bedroom with a walk-in closet, and brand-new carpets throughout. The exterior boasts a new roof within the last year, fresh paint, and new garage doors for enhanced durability and curb appeal. The 3-car garage provides ample space. The fenced backyard with a composite deck ensures privacy and offers a scenic retreat for gatherings or quiet moments. What sets this property apart is the expansive possibilities - offering loads of space for RV parking, boats, ATVs, and all kinds of recreational toys. Embrace the freedom to indulge in your outdoor adventures with the convenience of keeping your vehicles and gear right on your property. A tranquil escape within reach of everyday amenities and the renowned Dayton Valley Golf Course.
